des: "Juicing and making fruit and veggie smoothies is a wonderful way for your body to get those nutrients it needs during the day. This smoothie has some great flavors in it and is healthy for you!"
ins: Blend spinach, beet, yogurt, raspberries, blueberries, ice cubes, and cucumber together in a blender until smooth.
